high_descs: turn left and look down at the bin.
Take out the potato inside the bin.
Turn around and take a step forward and turn left. Take a couple steps and turn to the left facing the microwave.
Place the potato standing up inside the microwave. Take the potato back out.
Turn to the right and walk straight half way and turn right to go towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the potato on the very top shelf and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: To move a heated potato from the microwave to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left to face the trash bin.
Take the potato from the trash bin.
Turn around, then turn left, move forward, then turn left to go to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn right, move forward, turn right at the stove, then go straight to the fridge.
Put the potato on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the fridge.

high_descs: turn left to the trash bin
take the potato out of the trash bin
open the microwave, put the potato in, heat the potato, take the potato out
turn around, walk to the refrigerator
put the potato in the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: cook the potato from trash bin in the microwave, put it in the refrigerator
